FBIS4-35598 "drnes106_g_94005" FBIS-NES-94-106 Daily Report 1 Jun 1994 Sudan Ummah Party Leaders, Activists Arrested Ummah Party Leaders, Activists Arrested NC0106184094 Cairo MENA in English 1715 GMT 1 Jun 94 NC0106184094 Cairo MENA English BFN [Text] Cairo, June 1 (MENA)--Sudanese security authorities have launched a large-scale arrest campaign against leaderships and activists of the opposition Ummah Party. The arrests, carried out on May 19, included a number of former ministers and key officials as well as university professors who are affiliated with the Ummah Party, according to a statement faxed to MENA today. Families of the detainees were denied access to information on their whereabouts, the statement added.
